reviewText: Great film! Good quality! Husband wanted it and was happy I found at a great price! This is one of his favorites!
So awesome. I love that movie and it arrived in a timely fashion and in perfect condition. I am very pleased.
The item arrived as promised in time to be wrapped for Christmas...one of my friend's favorite gifts
Movie skips through out the whole thing. Ive had booylegs that work better than this movie. Definitely unsatisfying.
exactly as it was described by seller, very happy with my purchase!
